{"title":"MySql","uid":"9575e4b650941f02c5b9a1d623012ff0","slug":"Database/MySql","date":"2020-04-15T13:07:04.000Z","updated":"2022-04-06T09:13:39.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Database/MySql.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/mysql.jpeg","content":"<h1 id=\"MySQL自增主键归零\"><a href=\"#MySQL自增主键归零\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MySQL自增主键归零\"></a>MySQL自增主键归零</h1><p><strong>直接清空所有数据，并将自增字段恢复从1开始计数：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">truncate table table_name;</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>没有truncate的权限时且曾经的数据不需要时：</strong></p>\n<p>   1）删除原有主键：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">ALTER TABLE &#39;table_name&#39; DROP &#39;id&#39;;</code></pre>\n\n<p>   2）添加新主键：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">ALTER TABLE &#39;table_name&#39; ADD &#39;id&#39; int(11) NOT NULL FIRST;</code></pre>\n\n<p>  3）设置新主键：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">ALTER TABLE &#39;table_name&#39; MODIFY COLUMN &#39;id&#39; int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,ADD PRIMARY KEY(id);</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"视图\"><a href=\"#视图\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"视图\"></a>视图</h1><p>在 SQL 中，视图是基于 SQL 语句的结果集的可视化的表。视图包含行和列，就像一个真实的表。视图中的字段就是来自一个或多个数据库中的真实的表中的字段。我们可以向视图添加 SQL 函数、WHERE 以及 JOIN 语句，我们也可以提交数据，就像这些来自于某个单一的表。</p>\n<h2 id=\"NOTE：\"><a href=\"#NOTE：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"NOTE：\"></a>NOTE：</h2><ol>\n<li>视图是虚表,它在存储时只存储视图的定义,而没有存储对应的数据</li>\n<li>视图只在刚刚打开的一瞬间,通过定义从基表中搜集数据,并展现给用户</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"创建视图\"><a href=\"#创建视图\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建视图\"></a>创建视图</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">CREATE VIEW name AS\n    SELECT .... FROM....</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"查看视图\"><a href=\"#查看视图\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看视图\"></a>查看视图</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">SHOW CREATE VIEW name</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"视图使用\"><a href=\"#视图使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"视图使用\"></a>视图使用</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">SELECT * FROM name</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"索引\"><a href=\"#索引\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"索引\"></a>索引</h1><p>定义：索引，使用索引可快速访问数据库表中的特定信息。索引是对数据库表中一列或多列的值进行排序的一种结构。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>聚集索引：该索引中键值的逻辑顺序决定了表中相应行的物理顺序。该索引可以包含多个列（组合索引），就像电话簿按姓氏和名字进行组织一样——<code>汉语字典正文</code></li>\n<li>非聚集索引：该索引中索引的逻辑顺序与磁盘上行的物理存储顺序不同——<code>“部首表”+“检字表”查找某一汉字</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"创建索引\"><a href=\"#创建索引\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建索引\"></a>创建索引</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">CREATE [UNIQUE] [CLUSTERED|NONCLUSTERED] \n    INDEX index_name\n    ON &#123;table|view&#125; (column1 [ASC|DESC][,...])\n\n-- 为student在class列上创建cluster索引\nCREATE INDEX Class ON student(class)\nCREATE UNIQUE INDEX SCno ON SC(Sno ASC,Cno DESC);</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"查看索引\"><a href=\"#查看索引\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看索引\"></a>查看索引</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">show index from table</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"查看是否命中\"><a href=\"#查看是否命中\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看是否命中\"></a>查看是否命中</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">-- explain +sql语句\nexplain select * from student where name &#x3D; &#39;张三&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"删除索引\"><a href=\"#删除索引\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除索引\"></a>删除索引</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">DROP INDEX name on student</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u012954706/article/details/81241049?depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromBaidu-2&utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromBaidu-2\">索引的使用</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"DDL\"><a href=\"#DDL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"DDL\"></a>DDL</h1><h2 id=\"建立表\"><a href=\"#建立表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建立表\"></a>建立表</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">CREATE TABLE Person \n(\n    Id char(8) NOT NULL,\n    Fid char(8),\n    Age int CHECK(Age&gt;0),\n    City varchar(9) DEFAULT &#39;Sandnes&#39;,\n\n    PRIMARY KEY (Id),\n    FOREIGN KEY (Fid) REFERENCES Person(Id)\n);</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"修改表\"><a href=\"#修改表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改表\"></a>修改表</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">ALTER TABLE 表名\n    ADD 字段名 字段类型\n    ADD CONSTRAINT 约束名 表达式\n    ALTER COLUMN 字段名 类型\n    DROP COLUMN 字段名\n    DROP CONSTRAINT 约束名\n--[RESTRICT]: 限制 \n--[CASCADE] : 级联</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"删除表\"><a href=\"#删除表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除表\"></a>删除表</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">DROP TABLE 表名 [CASCADE]</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"DML\"><a href=\"#DML\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"DML\"></a>DML</h1><h2 id=\"增加记录\"><a href=\"#增加记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"增加记录\"></a>增加记录</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">INSERT INTO 表名[(字段1, 字段2)] VALUES(值1, 值2)</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"修改记录\"><a href=\"#修改记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改记录\"></a>修改记录</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">UPDATE 表名 SET 字段1&#x3D;值1, 字段2&#x3D;值2 [WHERE 条件表达式]</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"删除记录\"><a href=\"#删除记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除记录\"></a>删除记录</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">DELETE FROM 表名 [WHERE 条件表达式]</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"SQL函数\"><a href=\"#SQL函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SQL函数\"></a>SQL函数</h1><h2 id=\"日期\"><a href=\"#日期\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"日期\"></a>日期</h2><ul>\n<li>a.今天星期几： <code>select dayname(now())</code></li>\n<li>b.今天是这个月的第几天： <code>select dayofmonth(curtime())</code></li>\n<li>c.今天是这一年的第几天：<code>select dayofyear(curtime())</code></li>\n<li>d.时间延长2天：<ul>\n<li>Mysql： <code>select DATE_ADD(Date,INTERVAL 2 DAY)</code></li>\n<li>Sql Server： <code>select DATEADD(DAY,2,Date)</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>通配符</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>%</td>\n<td>替代一个或多个字符</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_</td>\n<td>仅替代一个字符</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[charlist]</td>\n<td>字符列中的任何单一字符</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[^charlist]或者[!charlist]</td>\n<td>不在字符列中的任何单一字符</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>快捷键</th>\n<th>注释</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Ctrl+shift+del</td>\n<td>全删</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ctrl k+c&#x2F;u</td>\n<td>注释&#x2F;取消</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ctrl+del&#x2F;backspace</td>\n<td>删词</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ctrl+c&#x2F;v</td>\n<td>默认选中当前行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>sp_columns Name</td>\n<td>查看表结构</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n","text":"MySQL自增主键归零直接清空所有数据，并将自增字段恢复从1开始计数： truncate table table_name; 没有truncate的权限时且曾经的数据不需要时： 1）删除原有主键： ALTER TABLE &#39;table_name&#39; DROP &#3...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Datebase","slug":"Datebase","count":5,"path":"api/categories/Datebase.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"SQL","slug":"SQL","count":1,"path":"api/tags/SQL.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#MySQL%E8%87%AA%E5%A2%9E%E4%B8%BB%E9%94%AE%E5%BD%92%E9%9B%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">MySQL自增主键归零</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">视图</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#NOTE%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">NOTE：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">创建视图</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">查看视图</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%BE%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">视图使用</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">索引</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">创建索引</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">查看索引</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%AD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">查看是否命中</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除索引</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#DDL\"><span class=\"toc-text\">DDL</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">建立表</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%A1%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">修改表</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E8%A1%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除表</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#DML\"><span class=\"toc-text\">DML</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">增加记录</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">修改记录</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除记录</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#SQL%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">SQL函数</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">日期</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Yveltal","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"并发与恢复","uid":"b78b087946b7debd555f5132e0794ce7","slug":"Database/并发与恢复","date":"2020-05-01T07:36:04.000Z","updated":"2022-04-06T09:13:39.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Database/并发与恢复.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/mysql.jpeg","text":"并发控制1.事务用户定义的一个数据库操作序列， 事务是并发控制的基本单位 ACID特性（原子性Atomicity、一致性Consistency、隔离性Isolation、持续性Durability） 2.并发控制封锁排他锁 (X锁、写锁) ：其他事务在T释放此锁之前不能读取和修改...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Datebase","slug":"Datebase","count":5,"path":"api/categories/Datebase.json"}],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Yveltal","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"Java多线程","uid":"f28cfaf59efbc91eff32a0d9fd1a9e43","slug":"Java/多线程","date":"2019-11-25T04:39:04.000Z","updated":"2022-04-06T09:13:39.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Java/多线程.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/java.jpeg","text":"线程状态转换 新建状态（New）：新创建了一个线程对象。 就绪状态（Runnable）：线程对象创建后，其他线程调用了该对象的start()方法。该状态的线程位于可运行线程池中，变得可运行，等待获取CPU的使用权。 运行状态（Running）：就绪状态的线程获取了CPU，执行程序...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.1k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Java.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"多线程","slug":"多线程","count":1,"path":"api/tags/多线程.json"}],"author":{"name":"Yveltal","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}